I. Siftly Help Docs (Knowledge Base Source)
This document is intended to be the primary context source you index into pgvector.

1) Email Summarization
Description: Siftly uses on-device AI to analyze and shorten long emails into a concise summary, helping users understand the content quickly without reading the entire message.

How to use:
Step 1: Open the Siftly app.
Step 2: Select the email you want to summarize.
Step 3: Tap the “Summarize” icon (book icon).
Step 4: The summary appears instantly at the top of the email.

Note: This feature works best for emails longer than 500 words.

2) Email Classification
Description: Siftly automatically labels incoming emails based on content and intent (e.g., Priority, Orders, Promotions, Personal, Urgent), helping you manage your inbox more effectively.

Setup:
Step 1: Go to Settings > Inbox Management.
Step 2: Enable “Auto Classification”.
Step 3: Customize labels in “Custom Labels”.

Privacy note: Classification is performed entirely on your device to protect privacy.

3) Email Drafting / Reply Assistance
Description: DeepSeek LLM helps users generate professional replies or draft new emails from a few keywords.

Drafting guide:
Step 1: Start a new email or reply to an existing one.
Step 2: Type your intent (e.g., “Confirm the meeting on Wednesday” or “Request a quote for product A”).
Step 3: Tap “Draft AI” (pen icon).
Step 4: Siftly generates a draft. You can adjust tone (formal, casual, urgent) before sending.

4) On-device AI and DeepSeek LLM
Description: Siftly uses the DeepSeek Large Language Model (LLM) and runs core AI features directly on your mobile device.

Benefits & limitations:
- Privacy: Your email data does not leave your device for AI processing.
- Speed: Processing is fast because it does not require cloud round-trips.
- Device requirements: At least 4GB RAM and a recent OS (iOS 16+ or Android 13+).
- Updates: The model is updated via app updates.

II. Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)
Use these questions to test the chatbot’s retrieval and generation quality.

