- How do I know whether my DeepSeek model has been updated?

Summarization
- How do I enable email summarization?
- Does summarization work for non-English emails?
- Can Siftly summarize a long email thread end-to-end?

Classification
- How does Siftly automatically classify incoming emails?
- Can I create custom classification labels?
- What should I do if Siftly misclassifies an email?

Drafting
- Can I ask Siftly to write in a formal or casual tone?
- Can I edit the draft after AI generates it?
- Can Siftly write a complete email from just a few keywords?
